  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dc0\u0dd4. 18\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dbd\u0dd4 \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dcf \u0daf\u0dda\u0dc1\u0dd3\u0dba \u0d86\u0daf\u0dcf\u0dba\u0db8\u0dca  \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dad\u0db8\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4 \u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db4\u0daf\u0dd2\u0d82\u0da0\u0dd2 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dba\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Au. Everyone over 18 must register with the Inland Revenue Department",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Presenting the interim budget, Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe said that all persons above the age of 18 must be registered with the Inland Revenue Department regardless of tax limits.",
        "\"In order to increase the revenue, the tax administration has to play a major role to increase the efficiency of tax collection, increase tax compliance and prevent tax evasion.",
        "In accordance with the existing requirements, it is proposed to introduce the requirement of mandatory registration with the Inland Revenue Department for all advantaged persons above the age of 18 regardless of the tax exemption limits."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "the Inland Revenue Department",
          "label": "ORG"
        }
      ],
